items.title: Post Temasek, Haldiram's adds Alpha Wave and IHC to ongoing equity raise
items.description: In India, Alpha Wave Global ( previously Falcon Edge Capital) has bet on firms like Swiggy, Lenskart, Dream 11, Chaayos, Biryani by Kilo , Ola and Policy Bazaar.

items.title: FICCI caution members as US indict firms dealing in fentanyl precursors
items.description: The U.S. Department of Justice alleges that the companies facilitated the transportation, concealment, and sale of these substances within the US, in violation of federal law.

items.title: GMR Airports' DIAL sharply raises user fee at Delhi airport from April 16
items.description: For departing passengers on international flights, the UDF has risen from Rs 129 to Rs 650 for economy class (403% rise) and Rs 810 for business class (527% rise). Those arriving via an international flight into New Delhi will have to pay a new UDF which was previously not charged separately, at Rs 275 for economy class and Rs 345 for business class.
